    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "A simple fix to this would be having some kind of AltPathSearchRadius thing in the yaml so we could tell the path finding AI of the units how wide an area they should search for another path if the main one is totally stopped up with units.\r\n\r\nAnd yes this is extremely annoying to say the least when I'm expecting my whole force to go through an area and not stupidly take a path to their deaths over a few of my other units being too stubborn to move out of their way. >.>"
